3170,/Hotel_Review-g186338-d195225-Reviews-or3170-London_Marriott_Hotel_County_Hall-London_England.html#REVIEWS,London Marriott Hotel County Hall Reviews,Loved the Marriott County Hall,The Marriott County Hall provided excellent accomodations for our family of three visiting London. The views toward the river are fantastic. The rooms are above average for what we have encountered in European hotels. The bathroom was more like what you would expect in an American hotel with large amounts of counter space. The room was also equipped with a small area which had a mirror and hair dryer so that our teen-age daughter could dry her hair without monopolizing the bathroom. The hotel is convenient to the Waterloo tube and train stations as well as the Westminster tube. The staff was very helpful and the restaurant was also nice. I would highly recommend this property.,None,4.0
